Welcome to my unofficial Lichess4545 stats site!












Season stats and awards ⟶

Current league statuses










Post-season: season 40 has ended, but registrations for the next season aren’t open yet.






Mid-season: Season 34 will end on 12 Feb.


Register




Post-season: season 31 has ended, but registrations for the next season aren’t open yet.




Community leagues: Infinite Quest is going strong, Series (90+30) is on Season 25 (ends May 2024), and the last season of Rapid Battle ended in October 2023. To find out more about all our leagues, check out the Lichess4545 overview.
